{"tid":2324927,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★Apple 印度廠房暴動  員工聯群結隊闖入廠搗亂　數千iPhone被竊","createTime":"2020-12-14T09:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T10:27:04.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9fd2999e7c63ea75b3ffb0f5bcae15af3af37693","tid":2324927,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"為蘋果公司（Apple Inc.）iPhone進行組裝的緯創（Wistron）在印度的廠房出事。它位於接近印度班加羅爾（Bangalore/ Bengaluru）廠房12月12日被破壞，不滿的員工聯群結隊闖入廠搗亂並搶走手機。印度政府透露，緯創損失43.7億盧比（約4.6億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士告訴台灣中央社記者，除了被破壞的1樓辦公設施，以及車輛與生產線上被竊走的數千部蘋果iPhone等財物損失外，事件導致廠房在聖誕節生產旺季必須停工2周，損失重大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/561522/%E7%B7%AF%E5%89%B5%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%BB%A0%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A52%E5%91%A8-%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%83iphone%E8%A2%AB%E7%AB%8A-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F561522%2F%25E7%25B7%25AF%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2581%259C%25E5%25B7%25A52%25E5%2591%25A8-%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%258D%2583iphone%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25AB%258A-%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5&d=WHMLQMiyWmfm849WKe725FIIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=afe27cbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/561522/%E7%B7%AF%E5%89%B5%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%BB%A0%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E5%81%9C%E5%B7%A52%E5%91%A8-%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%83iphone%E8%A2%AB%E7%AB%8A-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5</a>"},{"pid":"b68e2bf5d1d32d04740d6e71c2153a72f7b7cbcd","tid":2324927,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T09:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\